{"tid":10861,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"考牌遇失魂泥頭車切線　學神心慌衰咗","createTime":"2016-11-29T05:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T16:45:46.000Z","uid":7033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2578961bc4e5ac776e81bbefbc8b981cc5beddcf","tid":10861,"uid":7033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:55:51.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=DYYU8Ta0XMbK5ri5AdQ6j5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=15619378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】學神考牌與切線泥頭車相撞，差200米過唔到路試。今晨11時許，一名姓冼學神，租用一輛客貨車考路試，他載同考官沿鯉魚門道往油塘方向行駛，至迴旋處轉入欣榮街時，突有一輛泥頭車從右邊切線駛至，遭該車左邊車身撞及，右邊車頭損毀，考官見狀立即將車煞停，幸事件中無人傷。 <br />\n<br />\n冼先生事後表示，今次是第一次考車牌，「學咗18個鐘，諗住1 take pass。」只差200米便完成考試，惟未能成功，信心受到打擊，不過下次會繼續努力。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161129/mobile/bkn-20161129121323356-1129_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161129%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20161129121323356-1129_00822_001.html&d=DYYU8Ta0XMbK5ri5AdQ6j5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=2f19b4b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161129/mobile/bkn-20161129121323356-1129_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ec6c13798ab341ebc740cf3efb1beadb193ed182","tid":10861,"uid":11958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:01:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b710dd6bcf3fb01735ed4e027e1214a34541ee03","tid":10861,"uid":37241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:20:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=DYYU8Ta0XMbK5ri5AdQ6j5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=15619378\" target=\"_blank\">http://on.cc</a>東網專訊】學神考牌與切線泥頭車相撞，差200米過唔到路試。今晨11時許，一名姓冼學神，租用一輛客貨車考路試，他載同考官沿鯉魚門道往油塘方向行駛，至迴旋處轉入欣榮街時，突有一輛泥頭車從右邊切線駛至，遭該車左邊車身撞及，右邊車頭損毀，考官見狀立即將車煞停，幸事件中無人傷。 <br />\n<br />\n冼先生事後表示，今次是第一次考車牌，「學咗18個鐘，諗住1 take pass。」只差200米便完成考試，惟未能成功，信心受到打擊，不過下次會繼續努力。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161129/mobile/bkn-20161129121323356-1129_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161129%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20161129121323356-1129_00822_001.html&d=DYYU8Ta0XMbK5ri5AdQ6j5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=2f19b4b2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161129/mobile/bkn-20161129121323356-1129_00822_001.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c055a67a63ea9cafca50e7c261407326d4ced9ec","tid":10861,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:21:39.000Z","msg":"好彩有泥頭車, 阻止條友出黎渣車害人, 學多18個鐘先啦, 出迴旋處睇定d先嗎"},{"pid":"268319f3a5ee694bb4f68c84fbd3d7525accf595","tid":10861,"uid":2640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:22:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/9681?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/9681?ref=ios</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMatch"},{"pid":"81c10054d0ce7ed57bf365ab9759dc2b016ccbac","tid":10861,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:19:16.000Z","msg":"考生被人撞，錯不在考生。<br />\n點解要肥佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7899e28037237157f5bf8587c7dfbbfc3e2873c7","tid":10861,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:22:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好彩有泥頭車, 阻止條友出黎渣車害人, 學多18個鐘先啦, 出迴旋處睇定d先嗎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc565547a64565111150efff275425f0f63b274","tid":10861,"uid":1089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-1