 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日日都有人炒車 三車連炒要消防出動救人 到最後 有d賣紙都唔柒賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人揸車要急要快 趕住搵食做免死金牌嘛"},{"pid":"0991bbc72595fec295dc934c144b6f8eec3e7831","tid":10861,"uid":21861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:45:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一日一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日日都有人炒車 三車連炒要消防出動救人 到最後 有d賣紙都唔柒賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人揸車要急要快 趕住搵食做免死金牌嘛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nI mean 考牌車出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 琴日有位絲打考牌都撞左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92eb212879742eeda6fe43eab674734d9b70418","tid":10861,"uid":6935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:45:46.000Z","msg":"我今日都係考油塘，遲過佢考，考仁字圍返試場果時出迴旋處，我隔離個考官提埋我要行右線返，過左架死車先cut返左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw我個考官好似係相中人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}